You need to know that your collaborators have sufficient knowledge to execute the plan. The question is... what do you do when you look around the room and suddenly realize there's a gap in a very specific set of knowledge necessary to be effective?

... a minute later the doorbell rang and I opened it to find the teen's father standing there. He told me his son was autistic and it'd been hard for him to go trick-or-treating, and he said I'd just made his night. He was nearly in tears as he thanked me. 4/5

When anyone asks why I play up my tiny bit as an extra in the film... this is why. I am honored to have played a small part in adding a bright point in this kid's life, no matter how small. May the force be with him! 5/5
